  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>While engaged in combat with a creature whom the land of Iron considers a hostile entity, you manifest a blade of chakra with the intent to protect your own, and your countries honor. <br />This blade counts as a Martial Weapon, that deals 2d8 + Strength Modifier + Dexterity Modifier Slashing damage. <br />Has the Critical, Deadly, and Versatile(2d10) weapon properties. <br />Additionally, this weapon can be used for Bukijutsu with Slashing or Piercing Melee requirements.</p>",
